category: Member city/provincial sports association regulations/Article 33 (Organization and composition of city/provincial sports organizations)
contents: Article 33 (Organization and composition of city/provincial sports organizations) ① City/provincial sports organizations are organized into city/county/district sports organizations of which members are members. ② The organization and operation of city/provincial sports organizations are separately determined by the city/provincial sports association in accordance with the sports association’s ‘member sports group regulations’. Revised 2022. 5. 10.
